race.comment: CIAO BELLA MIA (11) win record hardly excites but did get off the mark here three starts ago. Launched late from the wide gate when a slashing fourth over 1200m at the Sapphire Coast. Drawn out again and gets the right tempo to finish strongly. GEOSTORM (10) tough old gelding holding his form. Kept fresh after battling in the soft (7) going when fourth over 1300m at this track. Will push forward and give a ton of cheek. GIOVANNA STAR (12) has come back much stronger this prep and doesn't have to improve much to win this. Strong through the line when third over 1200m at Warren. Look for her late. MISS BARILOCHE (1) kept fresh and drops sharply in class and trip today. Failed to handle city grade when a fading seventh over 1800m at Randwick in Midway class. . Has her share of ability and must be kept safe.
